examples/tiny_debug/checkpoints/*.pt
examples/tiny_debug/logs/*
examples/tiny_debug/outputs/*
!examples/tiny_debug/checkpoints/README.md
!examples/tiny_debug/logs/README.md
!examples/tiny_debug/outputs/README.md

